<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>109</hymn_number>
<title>Previous to the Ordinance ƲIT109</title>
<time_sig>S.M. (6.6.8.6.)</time_sig>
<aka>Ʋba Chihowa yʋt</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ʋba Chihowa yʋt
 Na̱ pim apesa ka
 Ithaiyanʋt, holitoblit,
 Isht il ahantashke.

[V2]
 Ʋlla pim a̱sha kʋt
 Immi biekʋshke,
 Isht il aiokpahancha he,
 Pim ahni tok oke.

[V3]
 Yʋmohmi pulla ho̱,
 Oka hanta yokʋt
 Isht a baptisma chi̱ hoka,
 Il im issa hoke.

[V4]
 Ʋba Shilombish ʋt
 Ʋlla chu̱kʋsh oka
 Chisʋs im issish hanta ka
 Isht baptismochashke.

[V5]
 Ʋba Pi̱ki oka
 Immi toba pullʋt
 Im antihi̱a hokbano;
 Il ahni fehnʋshke.

[V6]
 Pim ʋlla ilʋppa
 Chihi̱ma pi bʋnna,
 Pim ahninchit okchalinchí,
 Pi̱ki Chihowa ma!</lyrics>
</song>